11" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-recipe node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/recipes/chocolate-cherry-christmas-pudding"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe/recipe-image/2016/10/cherry-chocolate-pudding.jpg?itok=1aE5BWyD" width="468" height="382" alt="Chocolate &amp; cherry Christmas pudding 2016" title="Chocolate &amp; cherry Christmas pudding 2016" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Recipe</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Chocolate &amp; cherry Christmas pudding</h3><div class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-form-item"><div class="form-item form-type-item"><div class="field-main"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">4.642855</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="description"><p class="fivestar-summary fivestar-summary-">(7 <span class="rating-text"> ratings</span>)</p></div></div></div></div></div> </a></article><article id="node-93726" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-recipe node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/recipes/2711/cranberry-maple-and-pecan-pudding"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--3664_12.jpg?itok=JxfKOYyH" width="468" height="382" alt="Cranberry, maple &amp; pecan pudding" title="Cranberry, maple &am